   <tp:treatment-sec sec-type="distribution">
      <p>
Distribution
</p>
      <p>
         <tp:taxon-name>
Campanulina denticulata
</tp:taxon-name>
has an Indo-Pacific distribution (
Calder 2012
). Its bathymetric distribution extends from more than 
500 m
(Clarke 1970, as 
<tp:taxon-name>
Opercularella denticulata
</tp:taxon-name>
) to 
4040 m
deep (
Vervoort 1966
, as 
<tp:taxon-name>
O. denticulata
</tp:taxon-name>
).
</p>
